{"tid":1266254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"放眼未來 覺醒香港行動（特長文）","createTime":"2019-06-29T13:30:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T14:46:30.000Z","uid":260428,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"eefb3b14b6b0a3bdcf29721e0e33982138ebbcf9","tid":1266254,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T13:30:40.000Z","msg":"本人自從特首道歉後，開始政治醒覺。<br />\n開始追查歷史，睇下的官過去做左咩。<br />\n然後發現啲官立法會每次被人問，都會做一次錄音機，講大家聽啊媽係女人，我地部門嘅工作定義等等，<span style=\"color: gold;\">從無正面回應問題</span>。<br />\n<br />\n點解個個特首做都被人嘈？因為佢地做親嘅事真係<span style=\"color: blue;\">得個口講</span>以民為本，實際利益就肥上瘦下。仲成日講大話，搬弄數據，善用拖字訣。<br />\n<br />\n事例<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10161891552830022&amp;id=567620021\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10161891552830022%26id%3D567620021&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJoybpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=33a0aa7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10161891552830022&amp;id=567620021</a><br />\n<br />\n當然，唔係所有政策都衰，否則議會就唔會每年通過咁多議案。但一粒老鼠屎可以壞了一鍋粥，一個壞政策足以改變香港。<br />\n<br />\n最近注意到，香港暗中一步步被人收網，<br />\n1：大灣區發展<br />\n2：一簽多行<br />\n3：新聞操控<br />\n4：一地兩檢<br />\n5：送中條例<br />\n6：<span style=\"color: gold;\">中英條約，香港50年不變條款成了歷史文獻</span><br />\n7：智能電燈柱<br />\n8：TG網路攻擊<br />\n9：大範圍新式文宣工作<br />\n10：修改教育<br />\n還有更多。。<br />\n以上都係一步步，都可以香港人進行意識控制。<br />\n<br />\n政府用武力硬推政策，就失去大義。<br />\n所以政府用媒體造謠，輿論抹黑取得大義，例如80萬個簽名就話80萬人支持，數據一點都不嚴謹，就攞去國際宣傳。或者幹脆暗中進行，無人知就無人阻。<br />\n政府手段成功，只喺因為政治醒覺嘅人太小，唔識分析，大家無具體客觀數據，個個都話自己代表大部分人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">然而，真理係不能被洗腦抹去。</span><br />\n人類係世界嘅一份子，歐洲唔係歐洲人擁有，中國都唔係中國人擁有。地係屬於大家嘅，中共亦唔代表中國五千年嘅文化，不能代表中國人。正如一個黑警唔係全黑，一個暴力唔係全部暴徒。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">當你注意力集中係黑警打人，反送中嘅同時</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">請睇清楚有人在香港下盤大棋</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">請睇清楚有人在香港下盤大棋</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">請睇清楚有人在香港下盤大棋</span><br />\n大家不能坐待下一次又有XX條例，阻止已大遲。現在網絡已有水軍，甚至Ai水軍，黑客。<br />\n今次網絡自發組織成功，但下次會否被防護或被拆係未知之數。<br />\n黑警文宣都突然有進步左啦，仲有人被上門拘捕。日後有人偽造影片都唔出奇！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我不是什麼大人物，但懇請大家，特別係和理非鍵盤戰友</span><br />\n用客觀事例同身邊嘅人分享，教小朋友，教老人家！等佢哋見到報道，即時自己分析！<br />\n<br />\n1：分析數據真假，可信性。<br />\n2：分析報導嘅偏頗性<br />\n3：教佢地去揾出真相<br />\n4：官員嘅文字藝術<br />\n5：政策背後嘅魔鬼細節影響<br />\n6：參考過去背景<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港要一場文化大革命</span><br />\n港豬政治醒覺行動<br />\n<br />\n巿民識自行分析，自然會一齊上街。唔係次次睇到烈士被人打，被自殺先出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n我地係小巿民，無殺傷力，同警力裝備無得比，但我地有人，有堅持，有真理！<br />\n<br />\n人民服務政府？還是政府服務人民？<br />\n盤古初開，中國文化都係賢者助民。<br />\n香港從無分裂，資料足夠下人本性係識分對錯，莫要等大家無得上網先醒覺，遲了。<br />\n<br />\n日本韓國有自己文化壓力，<br />\n你又會想身邊嘅人，<br />\n子女受呢類思想禁忌壓力嗎？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n支持中國嘅朋友，<br />\n中國日後唔一定好似現在，<br />\n習佢可能現在係明君，但總有一日會死，<br />\n下個如果領導學金正X捉你個女做後宮。。。或者高官犯法，你都投訴無門(尋釁滋事 )<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/256668\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F256668&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJoybpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=d028f614\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/256668</a><br />\n如果中央話要香港做中國堆填區，你又可以點吖？<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果你係議員：</span><br />\n<br />\n近日二百萬上街，政府也可無視，<br />\n令人疑問怎樣才能表逹民意？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">個個議員官員都話「大多數巿民」認同<br />\n但無可靠數據</span><br />\n<br />\n現在的制度需要作出改變，<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔通次次都要大遊行，大家先會聽意見？</span><br />\n何況宜家唔聽<br />\n<br />\n世界科技今非昔<br />\n香港有多功能智慧燈柱<br />\n有八達通服務站領取公共交通費用補貼<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">加多個投票機得唔得吖？</span></span><br />\n1：大型爭議使用<br />\n2：身份證晶片一人一次<br />\n3：投票只有支持反對，論會共定題目<br />\n4：事件足夠文宣冷靜期，防止被媒體控制文意<br />\n5：同一文宣，兩方各自加入內容<br />\n6：教育加入公民投票思考課，了解如何分析文宣及事件的魔鬼細節。<br />\n7：投票結果不一定有約束力<br />\n8：結果要顯示年齡層（未來是年輕人的）<br />\n9：你幫手諗吓啦，<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">就算有真普選，個特首可以被收買架，咁多個利益團體總要取捨，到時又要人落台？大政策必先要有真諮詢！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多 謝 收 睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3952b6552968684aad1ae47ce591d32547e73e81","tid":1266254,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T14:48:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3a370c8f6f5dcf3c1baeefb91288f05bd6a18d5","tid":1266254,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T14:49:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a0ef947e548c230cd0d11c0c35513ba4ada0001c","tid":1266254,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:34:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"faaea11d2e2869cd20635361424557190fb5c906","tid":1266254,"uid":23738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:05:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87cdaabb965e17292381e98ebcec115b0bbfc6a3","tid":1266254,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T00:21:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1d0cb7619c6231663edad446229141ea2ccf7e83","tid":1266254,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T01:30:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"58d44c41e83a66adcde58c950646392b25ca7aed","tid":1266254,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T01:55:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6aaaf3593534bcb395bb997a69a88fe27d54d07d","tid":1266254,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T03:28:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bdf2cedad20424771f6a112ebc3a80b0f051a576","tid":1266254,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:17:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b92c8d2ced19cf63364ab2b57c301baf4e403e1b","tid":1266254,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T06:54:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"661ccd4eb597b1bf8f17ecc27716e5190ea415e4","tid":1266254,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T06:54:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8pAyEOY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8pAyEOY.jpg&h=6abdede8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[ 備戰 ] 夢境作戰訓話 + 整合Post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1267323/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1267323/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人到而家仲未識真正咁運用三角鐵馬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1267307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1267307</a>"},{"pid":"f87dec7060c6c8c2cf01fce7663eeb03f10d0d03","tid":1266254,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T08:54:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8a16f608757f9e2a37e33b6897581ea400e01b65","tid":1266254,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T08:58:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"84850a35dad6025cc33c32461d4126271d35184c","tid":1266254,"uid":264106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T09:43:37.000Z","msg":"仲有加強DQ非獻世派人員參選。"},{"pid":"369d4a20be7689f2e8d2969cf270da16d87abf51","tid":1266254,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T09:54:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bbedd930d91321950a62ef5fc27d5a27bb38f22e","tid":1266254,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:10:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5cea4da6703b1d01ab3d4decd511646d5005edda","tid":1266254,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:13:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"459f13609f82f5710e7451151e8a887ec840a42e","tid":1266254,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T22:30:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"905071145a878cde88e94bbf7b0f57867fee9f07","tid":1266254,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T23:57:38.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"2d8e3e79e8b412ca42d6b44570d42c3dcae9c9ea","tid":1266254,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T00:39:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cdb4ee96cd4d6bea80219817a19a277b71f98315","tid":1266254,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T02:26:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"afe352d817de09b7d28b89369530032aba34d986","tid":1266254,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T03:55:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"efefd9db39135a08027129c1ad8337b2aa6176e7","tid":1266254,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T03:59:47.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"d9b2276216bbd268635c43f267764a5f2db7c2f4","tid":1266254,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T14:46:30.000Z","msg":"推"}]}